            "id": 5969071,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大漲1.01%，報41528.24點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間08日11:28，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲414.27點（或1.01%），暫報41528.24點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.09%</li><li>近 1 月：+8.29%</li><li>近 3 月：-7.2%</li><li>近 6 月：-5.98%</li><li>今年以來：-3.36%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以華特迪士尼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DIS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DIS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DIS-US</a>)領漲。華特迪士尼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DIS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DIS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DIS-US</a>)上漲3.11%；波音(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BA-US</a>)上漲2.9%；高盛集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GS-US</a>)上漲2.48%；美國運通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AXP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AXP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AXP-US</a>)上漲2.27%；摩根大通銀行(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JPM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JPM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JPM-US</a>)上漲1.77%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，默克藥廠(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRK-US</a>)下跌1.55%；安進(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMGN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMGN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMGN-US</a>)下跌1.35%；沃爾瑪(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WMT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WMT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WMT-US</a>)下跌0.94%；麥當勞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MCD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MCD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MCD-US</a>)下跌0.81%；可口可樂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KO-US</a>)下跌0.74%。</p></section></main>",
